I agree with this....I am willing to whip up a good story line as I 
have been pondering on creating one anyways.  I agree, the end of 
NBWRPG is here, it was well while it lasted, but it is time to move 
on.  I can say that if we don't change something, I will be quiting 
the rpg for good.  I would love to move this along, to start again 
somewhere else where we don't have useless story's with dead 
ends.  If your with me, good on you, if not, I hope that in the end 
this rpg will work out cuz i will not be here.
